{"id": "ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ", "rating": 4.2, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 742, "displayName": {"text": "Kyung Bok Kung Korean BBQ", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Elegant space for a range of traditional Korean dishes including barbeque options.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoSVEySlZZVWgyTjNKNmJuY3pNMlphWmpZd1RGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "More than just Korean BBQ, this premium wagyu course felt like a complete fine dining experience. From beautifully prepared traditional appetizers to expertly grilled wagyu and comforting dishes to finish, every course was thoughtfully crafted. The quality of the beef, elegant presentation, and attentive service made this one of the most memorable Korean meals I’ve had in Southern California.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "More than just Korean BBQ, this premium wagyu course felt like a complete fine dining experience. From beautifully prepared traditional appetizers to expertly grilled wagyu and comforting dishes to finish, every course was thoughtfully crafted. The quality of the beef, elegant presentation, and attentive service made this one of the most memorable Korean meals I’ve had in Southern California.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Helen Jiahui Guo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110179487798926277614/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU52bRVwEIqKNohw5SdqbC30d82NljptHRT9WiKA3anK9T4yL6r=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T01:58:21.175085913Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoSVEySlZZVWgyTjNKNmJuY3pNMlphWmpZd1RGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoSVEySlZZVWgyTjNKNmJuY3pNMlphWmpZd1RGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd2b0a90b2d76b:0x4c88548415e92ed"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xodWMyNXlRWGRhV0hrelIyNHllVE01YjJzNGRYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is a total hidden gem Korean restaurant. High-end Korean dishes with wagyu beef which was amazing. The quality of the Wagyu was really high and I love their dishes. We went on a dinner time on the weekend and they were really busy. The service was excellent and great place to take a date. I would totally came back for dinner again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is a total hidden gem Korean restaurant. High-end Korean dishes with wagyu beef which was amazing. The quality of the Wagyu was really high and I love their dishes. We went on a dinner time on the weekend and they were really busy. The service was excellent and great place to take a date. I would totally came back for dinner again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "bros gear", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106491851330957575451/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXpT0MZWvGa1tUQN8KghwEy-9FI2Q8gEG3UwC1DffRLezkPA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-01T22:52:45.643368986Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xodWMyNXlRWGRhV0hrelIyNHllVE01YjJzNGRYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xodWMyNXlRWGRhV0hrelIyNHllVE01YjJzNGRYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dd2b0a90b2d76b:0x4c88548415e92ed"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kd1YwRnJRemR2TkVRMVEwczJPR3hyVVhOeGVVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I always order the K-BBQ course here, and it never fails to satisfy. You can choose your preferred cuts of meat—the boneless short rib (kkotsal) and galbi are both delicious, but the beef tongue is my absolute favorite. The soybean paste stew and cold noodles at the end are also fantastic. With great service and top-notch food, I think this is the best local spot for hosting guests. Make sure to make a reservation, as it gets quite busy!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I always order the K-BBQ course here, and it never fails to satisfy. You can choose your preferred cuts of meat—the boneless short rib (kkotsal) and galbi are both delicious, but the beef tongue is my absolute favorite. The soybean paste stew and cold noodles at the end are also fantastic. With great service and top-notch food, I think this is the best local spot for hosting guests. Make sure to make a reservation, as it gets quite busy!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christina Han", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112336385994844548084/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJWaYUaWczTcfpwiW3-uiYYFcylF806hOPwEMawuh0pBHhbUDw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-03T04:56:54.643482562Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kd1YwRnJRemR2TkVRMVEwczJPR3hyVVhOeGVVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kd1YwRnJRemR2TkVRMVEwczJPR3hyVVhOeGVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd2b0a90b2d76b:0x4c88548415e92ed"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFeVdHNURaMjVpT1RWTmIwZHpPVTk2YTFkek1tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "There aren’t many Korean restaurants that offer a true Han Jeong Sik experience, so we were excited to discover one in Buena Park, conveniently located near Knott’s Berry Farm. To celebrate my brother’s special birthday lunch, we chose Kyoung Bok Kung and decided on the VVIP Han Jeong Sik for four.\nFrom beginning to end, the service was excellent, especially from a young gentleman named Devin, who was warm, attentive, and proactive. Once he understood that this was a birthday celebration and what our expectations were, he went above and beyond to make the experience memorable. Each course was thoughtfully served in sequence, from appetizers to dessert tea, with clear explanations from the menu. The dishes paired beautifully with my brother’s favorite Kikusui sake, which elevated the entire dining experience. One small note is that a few of the side bites, such as the jeon and jjigae, were slightly on the salty side, and I was also hoping to see white kimchi (baek kimchi) included. That said, these were minor points in an otherwise wonderful meal.\n\nA truly touching moment came when Devin learned it was my brother’s birthday, he surprised us with a special plate of miyeok-guk, the traditional Korean birthday soup. It was an incredibly thoughtful gesture and a delightful surprise for all of us. Overall, this was a refined and memorable Han Jeong Sik experience. I hope that a restaurant with such a strong reputation and high-quality Korean cuisine continues striving for perfection and ongoing improvement.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "There aren’t many Korean restaurants that offer a true Han Jeong Sik experience, so we were excited to discover one in Buena Park, conveniently located near Knott’s Berry Farm. To celebrate my brother’s special birthday lunch, we chose Kyoung Bok Kung and decided on the VVIP Han Jeong Sik for four.\nFrom beginning to end, the service was excellent, especially from a young gentleman named Devin, who was warm, attentive, and proactive. Once he understood that this was a birthday celebration and what our expectations were, he went above and beyond to make the experience memorable. Each course was thoughtfully served in sequence, from appetizers to dessert tea, with clear explanations from the menu. The dishes paired beautifully with my brother’s favorite Kikusui sake, which elevated the entire dining experience. One small note is that a few of the side bites, such as the jeon and jjigae, were slightly on the salty side, and I was also hoping to see white kimchi (baek kimchi) included. That said, these were minor points in an otherwise wonderful meal.\n\nA truly touching moment came when Devin learned it was my brother’s birthday, he surprised us with a special plate of miyeok-guk, the traditional Korean birthday soup. It was an incredibly thoughtful gesture and a delightful surprise for all of us. Overall, this was a refined and memorable Han Jeong Sik experience. I hope that a restaurant with such a strong reputation and high-quality Korean cuisine continues striving for perfection and ongoing improvement.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Xavier K", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106667355305306471721/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXULRzCa_Muo6R6Fr_CUp-sDtY7U2kSzTZ7omiw8MBoXG2WmxdSUw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-29T23:39:44.772066784Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFeVdHNURaMjVpT1RWTmIwZHpPVTk2YTFkek1tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFeVdHNURaMjVpT1RWTmIwZHpPVTk2YTFkek1tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dd2b0a90b2d76b:0x4c88548415e92ed"}, {"name": "places/ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pORk9YSXhNVnBsWDBKd2VHMVhRME01YlVKbGFWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Luxury, high-end Korean charcoal BBQ (at table) with set menus perfect for big group dining.\n\nStylish and refined, the interior displays a modern update on traditional Korean — reminiscent of Seoul’s Gangnam District. Private dining rooms available. Highly attentive and professional service, perfect for assisting with grilling.\n\nEnjoy the top-quality beef bbq, with the Small Portion Cold Buckwheat Noodle (후식 물냉면) — an LA Koreatown tradition that made a reverse migration and became popular in the old country. Other highlights include Spicy Seasoned Skate Fish (홍어무침), perfect on heat and vinegar.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Luxury, high-end Korean charcoal BBQ (at table) with set menus perfect for big group dining.\n\nStylish and refined, the interior displays a modern update on traditional Korean — reminiscent of Seoul’s Gangnam District. Private dining rooms available. Highly attentive and professional service, perfect for assisting with grilling.\n\nEnjoy the top-quality beef bbq, with the Small Portion Cold Buckwheat Noodle (후식 물냉면) — an LA Koreatown tradition that made a reverse migration and became popular in the old country. Other highlights include Spicy Seasoned Skate Fish (홍어무침), perfect on heat and vinegar.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christopher Chung", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105905503230032407795/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_TX2BSsc9liPsGKqwvhTN9hxq5DMtaY0ZxvVWGYWfTuIK_pk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-26T17:46:02.901093756Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pORk9YSXhNVnBsWDBKd2VHMVhRME01YlVKbGFWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pORk9YSXhNVnBsWDBKd2VHMVhRME01YlVKbGFWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd2b0a90b2d76b:0x4c88548415e92ed"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJa9eykAor3YAR7ZJeQUiFyAQ/photos/AWCwydhNgWogybnvPdeW3PxrBsfAqSVnCiizWMQ0W3OoSlAt5Ti2MGyHLJOA7_cjoWh9V3N9AKfDQ7aeEImtnAR4tpwPpK6UfMYPltZZbNvi2yAon1UVLVGSVRRObLNswhvqO3vXE48Brgn3TlNvVi7c5-BsGO6mwbiBxX6J572c704nvQpf944FPZTNGJanSw_OrESMkhb